title: Lukid - Discography (2007--2012)
description:
All albums (and extras) from London producer Lukid (Luke Blair.)
All songs are 320 and ripped from my CD collection except the album Chord, which is from Amazon and has VBR, and the non album tracks, which Iv'e collected from all over the internet over the last few years.  Fans of Flying Lotus and underground styled psychedelic hip-hop beats will enjoy Lukid's unique sound and variety.


Contents:
---------

1. Onandon (2007)
2. The Now EP (2007)
3. Foma (2009)
4. Chord (2010)
5. Non-Album Tracks (2008-2010)
6. GLUM EP (2011)
7. Lonely At The Top (2012)
8. This Dog Can Swim EP
9. Live Mixes (2009,2012)
